            <zone forceUpdate='true' h='39750' id='17' type-v2='text' w='20000' x='79167' y='59000'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Conclusions</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>1. States with more firearm laws show lower homicide rates and gun ownership levels.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>2. Evidence based laws correlate with the lowest homicide rates.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>3. Laws passed outweighs gun ownership as a predictor, evidence based law states maintain low homicide rates even at higher ownership levels.</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
